  "title": "After reading the doc for url sync, I have no idea how it works.",
  "body": "The doc says to define an array of string for the parameters i want to track in the url.\n\nSo I came up with: `urlSync: {\n    trackedParameters: ['query','cost','set']\n  }` but it didn't work so I went to the full documentation (helper) where I found that maybe I should use 'disjunctiveFacet:['cost',...]' but... from here I've stopped.\n\nI guess it miss an example.\n",
